summary: This mod changes the music in player homes to have a more homey feels while still feeling lore friendly.
descriptionHtml:
This mod changes the music in player homes to have a more homey feels while still feeling lore friendly. This mod changes the music in the following Player Homes:Breezehome

Honeyside
Proudspire Manor
Severin Manor
Vlindrel Hall
Windstad Manor
Lakeview Manor
Heljarchen Hall
